{"tid":2373584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日過左呀嫲度飲湯....","createTime":"2021-01-20T14:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T17:43:25.000Z","uid":315329,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26a791e680ebcc4e73d12630c8523ea25565e3eb","tid":2373584,"uid":315329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"飲飲下佢冇啦啦拎左個豬嘅下顎骨出嚟,話早兩日捕到隻<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">野豬</span></strong></span></strong>,係呢個時候我仲未察覺有啲咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直到差唔多我<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">飲哂</span></span></strong>之際,啲老人家好鍾意講啲湯有幾靚㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟然講到<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">有豬肺係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我就知仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我笑笑口咁問佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今次個豬肺係買番嚟定係劏架?<br />\n佢又笑笑口咁答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今係<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">劏</span></span></span></strong>嘅。<br />\n<br />\n我當堂哭撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個腦已經直接skip咗好嬲好嬲嗰個狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係識得傻笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要啲姑姐喺我隔離話一早知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係哭撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我依家懷住好無奈嘅心情行緊返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手上面仲拎住咗壺野生豬肺湯話叫我拎返去畀阿媽飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該話畀阿媽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係等佢飲左啖再同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a57bdb2ea965265183d6a94e443e7e5a0bd082b","tid":2373584,"uid":315329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:22:26.000Z","msg":"今晚會唔會夢到野豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317beba30f0cdf95602ab6ea42549b2ae2901d9b","tid":2373584,"uid":315329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"我會唔會死㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc3264c3d9c793f50a11385fa9a0e03a2798b43","tid":2373584,"uid":56940,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"CLS 唔知有幾多菌<br />\n變種武肺"},{"pid":"160589df46e8515ccf4972168bfcc4e43f0e83b3","tid":2373584,"uid":202354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"11e7f5148b6fb270c3304ed2f27af3451f2fc8a3","tid":2373584,"uid":306304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"祝樓主下世好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68278c91f1d09c34aa6ed1a451e09ab91aaf1578","tid":2373584,"uid":315329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc3264c3d9c793f50a11385fa9a0e03a2798b43","tid":2373584,"uid":56940,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"CLS 唔知有幾多菌<br />\n變種武肺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"香港野豬冇事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8610a1e9eba03a082718e09618ba84953e61f758","tid":2373584,"uid":252920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"SARS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5069124caab8bb027620d8502f32fac1a68d81f7","tid":2373584,"uid":8948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bfc3264c3d9c793f50a11385fa9a0e